Class AuthorizationTicketUpdateResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.authlete.common.dto.ApiResponse
      • com.authlete.common.dto.AuthorizationTicketUpdateResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    public class AuthorizationTicketUpdateResponse
extends ApiResponse
    Response from Authlete's /auth/authorization/ticket/update API.

    The API is used to update information about a ticket that has been issued from the /auth/authorization API.

    Since:
    3.88, Authlete 3.0
